<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.2.5">
<l>ceykiṉṟa teṉkaṇṇuk koṉṟē yokkiṉṟa tivvula kattu</l>
<l>vaikuntaṉ pūtaṅka ḷēyāy māyatti ṉāleṅku maṉṉi</l>
<l>aiyamoṉ ṟillai yarakka racurar piṟantīruḷ ḷīrēl</l>
<l>uyyum vakaiyillai toṇṭī rūḻi peyarttiṭuṅ koṉṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Something is done to my eye. It suits this world.</l>
<l>By māyā staying everywhere as bhūtas of the one from Vaikunta</l>
<l>there is not one doubt. If you are those who are born as rakṣasa and asura,</l>
<l>there is no way of escaping, slaves. The aeon kills [and] returns.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
